<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HGO00"> Committee on Oversight and Government Reform</committee-name>: </header><text>Mr. Gowdy, Chair.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> </section> </resolution-body> <resolution-body style="multiple-resolved-clause" id="H9E3C23CCA9334E92A2404F89212F60E1"> <section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="H9C7144E1B91D44EF8D237113121A4991"><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">That the following named Member be, and is hereby, ranked as follows on the following standing committee of the House of Representatives:</text> 

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HGO00"> Committee on Oversight and Government Reform</committee-name>: </header><text>Mr. Chaffetz, after Mr. Jordan.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> </section> </resolution-body> <attestation><attestation-group><attestor display="no">Karen L. Haas,</attestor><role>Clerk.</role></attestation-group></attestation> </resolution> 

